txt.en: You have reached level 15 and now may purchase a personal home. For prices and availability visit a Classic Housing Broker near Michel Delving, Thorin's Hall, Duillond, or South Bree, or a Premium Housing Broker in Dol Amroth or Minas Tirith. Premium Housing upkeep is waived for VIPs.\n\nFeel free to visit all the neighbourhoods before deciding where to settle down. Once you own a house, you can enjoy extra storage and have fun decorating!
